# Common spreadsheet/data dumps
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.csv
*.tsv
*.parquet
*.feather
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.mat

# Data (keep demo only)
data/*
!data/README.md
!data/demo/
!data/demo/**

# Local-only screening modules
/src/screening/